25 Floor Amend 1 AM 47 0146
ADOPTED
Senator Jackson of the 41st offered the following amendment #1:
1 Amend SB 350 (LC 47 3652) by replacing "75%" on lines 25 and 26 with "80%".
2 By replacing "31.984326641319%" on line 33 with "32%".
3 By replacing lines 47 through 50 with the following:
4 (a) The annual salary of the Clerk of the State Court of DeKalb County shall be 90 percent
5 of the annual salary received by the Clerk of the Superior Court of DeKalb County.
6 By replacing lines 57 through 65 with the following:
7 Each judge of the State Court, Magistrate Court, Probate Court, or Juvenile Court of
8 DeKalb County and each non-judicial official who pursuant to this Act receives any
9 compensation from DeKalb County funds shall also receive from DeKalb County the same
10 fringe benefits provided to all county employees, including but not limited to health
11 insurance, dental insurance, vision insurance, life insurance, flexible benefits, incentives,
12 and longevity pay. Each judge or official may opt out of any such fringe benefit. Such
13 fringe benefits shall be calculated based upon the total years of service that the judge or
14 official has provided as a judge, official, or employee of DeKalb County and shall be
15 calculated based upon the judge's or official's total compensation from state or DeKalb
16 County funds. Nothing in this section shall be construed to modify or affect any pension
17 or retirement plan."
